    "extract": "Afya Foundation is a 501(c)(3) not-for-profit organization based in Yonkers, New York. It was founded in 2007 by Danielle Butin, MPH, OTR after a trip to Tanzania, where she encountered the dire circumstances and severely limited medical resources of their medical clinics. Afya, which means \"good health\" in Swahili seeks to spread \"Good Health Through Giving,\" and does so by providing medical supplies, consumables, sustainable equipment, and community outreach supplies to international health clinics."
